headline: AM Best Assigns Indicative Issue Credit Ratings to MetLife, Inc.'s New Shelf Registration
summary: AM Best has assigned indicative Long-Term Issue Credit Ratings of 'a-' to senior unsecured issues, 'bbb+' to subordinated issues, and 'bbb' to preferred stock to the recently filed shelf...
